lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>during the recovery period after injury - the essence of the
method consists in gluing special cotton elastic bands that improve
microcirculation, reduce pain and swelling, improve muscle tone and simulate
